msgctxt "Talk00"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Oh! You're the guy who found the\n"
"<2.se_co>Great Fairy Fountain<3.re_co>!<4.pa> Funny running\n"
"into you here. Are you traveling too?\n"
"I've traveled all over the world,\n"
"so I'm happy to tell you about\n"
"new places, if you want."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (long)
msgctxt "Talk01"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Wow... What a dignified structure!<2.pa>\n"
"How does nature create such\n"
"magnificence?"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: choice
msgctxt "Talk02"
msgid ""
"<1.so>If you have a picture to show me,\n"
"let's see it already!<2.ch>"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: set_colour (blue)
#. 3: reset_colour
#. 4: sound
#. 5: set_colour (blue)
#. 6: reset_colour
#. 7: pause (short)
msgctxt "Talk03"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Hmm... This picture shows <2.se_co>Hyrule Castle<3.re_co>\n"
"in the distance.\n"
"\n"
"<4.so>They say there used to be a stage where\n"
"knighting ceremonies were performed,\n"
"just south of <5.se_co>Hyrule Castle<6.re_co>.\n"
"It's in ruins now, but...<7.pa>I'm pretty certain\n"
"that's what's in this picture."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (short)
msgctxt "Talk04"
msgid ""
"<1.so>I see.<2.pa> Well, if you ever need my help,\n"
"the offer stands. After all, you helped\n"
"me out a great deal!"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (short)
msgctxt "Talk05"
msgid ""
"<1.so>However...<2.pa>that area is extremely\n"
"dangerous. If you're planning on\n"
"going there, please be careful."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: choice
msgctxt "Talk08"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Hey! It's you! Did you come by to show\n"
"me that fabulous picture again?<2.ch>"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
msgctxt "Talk09"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Hey! We meet again. Are you out\n"
"traveling as well?\n"
"\n"
"I've traveled all over the world,\n"
"so I'm happy to tell you about\n"
"new places, if you want."
msgstr ""

