msgctxt "Talk10"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Hm? And you are?<2.pa> Sorry, but...\n"
"are you traveling too?\n"
"\n"
"I'm a painter, you see. I'm traveling the\n"
"world in search of beautiful scenery.\n"
"\n"
"<3.so>They say the most beautiful spots in\n"
"the world are these places called\n"
"<4.se_co>Great Fairy Fountains<5.re_co>.\n"
"Not only are they incredibly beautiful,\n"
"but they supposedly can grant people\n"
"some kind of strange power...\n"
"<6.so>Sadly, I've yet to find one.<7.ra><8.so>But I heard a rumor "
"recently that there's\n"
"one near Kakariko Village!\n"
"\n"
"<9.so>Kakariko Village is my hometown.\n"
"Perhaps it's time for a visit..."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: set_colour (red)
#. 3: reset_colour
#. 4: pause (long)
msgctxt "Talk11"
msgid ""
"<1.so>A <2.se_co>Great Fairy Fountain <3.re_co>near\n"
"Kakariko Village...<4.pa> Could the rumor\n"
"be true?"
msgstr ""

