msgctxt "Talk12"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Hm? <2.pa>You...<3.pa> I'm sorry, but have we met\n"
"somewhere before?\n"
"\n"
"Well, it's not important. <4.pa>Have you ever\n"
"heard of a <5.se_co>Great Fairy Fountain<6.re_co>?\n"
"\n"
"<7.so>They say <8.se_co>Great Fairy Fountains<9.re_co> are\n"
"some of the most beautiful places\n"
"in the world!\n"
"Not only are they incredibly gorgeous,\n"
"but they can supposedly grant people\n"
"some kind of strange power...\n"
"<10.so>Sadly, I've yet to find one.<11.ra><12.so>But I heard a rumor "
"recently that there's\n"
"one near Kakariko Village!\n"
"\n"
"<13.so>Kakariko Village is my hometown.\n"
"Perhaps it's time for a visit..."
msgstr ""

